{"tid":1433990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗記者會語言偽術陰招","createTime":"2019-08-08T15:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:59:15.000Z","uid":255419,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9a562cfd4d7a22444087588e46b336fb55e02f20","tid":1433990,"uid":255419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"作為一個p牌廢中，我只係可以發夢玩下索帶，我真係唔可以講話可以幫到咩手，但我好希望響輿論戰出一分力去拆解而家果d 垃圾記者會既一啲陰招，作出分析整理，當佢地出陰招時盡量唔好跌入佢地陷阱度。<br />\n<br />\n1. 改詞換字<br />\n其實呢一樣係一開始政府話係暴動定係示威果陣，已經用緊呢啲方法帶輿論。<br />\n對佢地輿論有利就會加<br />\n-而家針對示威者，佢地會叫做暴徒<br />\n-鐳射筆本身有哂統稱既叫法，係要自行改稱鐳射槍，令公眾覺得係更具攻擊性，被問及名稱由來又答唔出<br />\n<br />\n對於佢地不利既事就加以淡化或歪曲<br />\n-催淚彈無啦啦改左做催淚煙<br />\n-明明元朗白衫斬人係巿民被單方面無差別襲擊，佢就形容為係有兩班人打鬥，令到成件事聽落好似頭兩個警員離開現場增援比較合理化<br />\n-記者多次影到警察刻意有目的地用強光照射記者，但被警方強行改為「意外」照射到記者<br />\n<br />\n2. 弱化問題<br />\n「其實之前已經答左」，「正如我剛才所講」聽到呢啲開頭既作答，其實俾觀眾感覺係果條問題係重覆左，所以唔係重點。但我想講我相信每一位記者問既問題都有佢既獨特性，重覆問題你地唔會問，問題係因為佢地罐頭答案係得果幾個，同埋為左避重就輕，就刻意理解條問題係重覆，然後好合理化咁重覆返罐頭答案。記者朋友如果聽到一半唔對路，可能要即刻stop 佢並講清楚問題重點，而唔係重覆，因為佢地重覆緊答案既時候，亦都係佢地浪費緊問答環節時間既方法，令自己答少啲問題。我見有記者朋友開始會用利君雅式追問法黎截停班友講野，我個人十分認同呢個做法。<br />\n<br />\n3. 話手頭上冇資料答唔到<br />\n當有啲問題佢地俾唔到答案出黎，可以提出叫佢地承諾聽日記者會主動交代，唔需要再浪費問答環節時間，如果唔係又質質膊冇左件事<br />\n<br />\n4. 單方面講就係<br />\n-話操普通話既警察傳言係假，而家完全唔佩戴委任證，到底佢地有咩證據話唔係？點樣服眾？<br />\n-某狗響高處掟出黎既唔係煙花係催淚煙，其實我建議係咪可以自行播片俾佢地睇即場反駁<br />\n<br />\n5. 開始理虧時，會叫你地去警察投訴科<br />\n如果講得呢句，其實佢地心知不妙，就算知其實自己錯都唔會道歉，直接彈你去冇可能成功既投訴黑洞了事，呢個時候可以加以追擊。<br />\n<br />\n6. 俾果個主持牽住鼻走<br />\n當記者問左一啲問題果2條友答唔到既時候，台下就會狂追問，主持見到咁就會話「剛才已經答左你問題」/「你地咁樣係進行唔到記者會」/「到下一位問問題」，嘗試去為台上兩條友解圍，而我睇係次次都解到，記者又真係好聽話咁停哂，俾下一位問。好多次都係就黎迫到佢答，就俾主持解左圍。其實記者朋友可唔可以到你發問時都講返，叫台上答左個追問先？個情況就好似玩街機槍game，有三個人玩，一個人輸左就下一個接力玩，玩到第二個人輸左要continue 既時候，第三個等到continue 時間過左要重頭黎過咁呀！！<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講，過期催淚彈呢一樣野係班狗拆唔掂既野，一定要加以追擊，因為有哂相。<br />\n同埋追究委任證問題，冇戴委任證其實好多野都會變得十分可疑。"},{"pid":"f83f7897e57425f034004011182f0b881a7cb45d","tid":1433990,"uid":1655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97235bfc7270a079c94802218af47c3f1d584bab","tid":1433990,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"Ush"},{"pid":"0122f56f00f36568e354d1f9deb2621271f114c3","tid":1433990,"uid":255419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e076433ebd48e9edd4c9bdd87265391b5dcfca0c","tid":1433990,"uid":255419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:09:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"505e5bbdbc39dbcc6f5522a250f7510258c0e879","tid":1433990,"uid":255419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:15:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4a0fa7f2aa7fd13555efadcd220cf5e2f258c40","tid":1433990,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:16:28.000Z","msg":"今日expired tear gas 都唔敢講"},{"pid":"945a2dc33ce0b4b451089926a8ec5b315b1b4024","tid":1433990,"uid":260906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:21:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10b56bc42378bd0603a8089253e13400c260b221","tid":1433990,"uid":15625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n高汁po"},{"pid":"40b8a28b8400a4b500fb8e2ffe0b6ac39fb3485d","tid":1433990,"uid":225455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:45:11.000Z","msg":"聽日記者會再問<br />\n有定無 用過期催淚彈<br />\n同佢講如果搭多過一個字既 就一定會再追問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc89a9d7c2833692b3afcc38c6dba0816b965a84","tid":1433990,"uid":225455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:45:13.000Z","msg":"聽日記者會再問<br />\n有定無 用過期催淚彈<br />\n同佢講如果搭多過一個字既 就一定會再追問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a39b33d0cb31bc9ccbff44a8bdcfb204741fcd","tid":1433990,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:51:19.000Z","msg":"[記者入］特首每次都轉移視線，希望到時有記者幫手問以下問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434292</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n互推下幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6af9599809a4f1211897f30ec58ad8b2ae65c05","tid":1433990,"uid":255419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4a0fa7f2aa7fd13555efadcd220cf5e2f258c40","tid":1433990,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:16:28.000Z","msg":"今日expired tear gas 都唔敢講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:27:42.000Z","msg":"事前一定有com 過唔可以響任何程況提「過期」呢兩隻字"},{"pid":"5189c92e95842293e49df9a672e8be6ccb72f8cc","tid":1433990,"uid":255419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:15:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5312f810329f4adf2640f591d24e6d00637053f","tid":1433990,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:24:03.000Z","msg":"但班狗支旗十幾年黎都係寫催淚煙 呢個真係佢地叫法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf70247ec7dee3a45ba5c214037b83b384d4305e","tid":1433990,"uid":255419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5312f810329f4adf2640f591d24e6d00637053f","tid":1433990,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:24:03.000Z","msg":"但班狗支旗十幾年黎都係寫催淚煙 呢個真係佢地叫法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:11:13.000Z","msg":"呢樣又真...不過其實都好易俾佢地含糊其詞<br />\n黑旗「警告 催淚煙」之後又真係會有催淚煙出現<br />\n只係「發射」就一定要用「催淚彈」<br />\n但「使用」就可以用「催淚煙」"},{"pid":"12c5fd79d265f077f2e95c65a232c2a70d1011a2","tid":1433990,"uid":255419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:09:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3be9efb4964f6b854bbf3dc782a33cd77e2da67","tid":1433990,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"推第6點"},{"pid":"e2b98bdaef268f5421a20b437f09cd420e27cd36","tid":1433990,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74369f9ae8437658a05da368b874e67bc4b8a411","tid":1433990,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:29:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5998adec7a5f9907014de0450d449239423e741b","tid":1433990,"uid":176996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8974aefc0f542d1f616a91708e7728274d68d37a","tid":1433990,"uid":238613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"認同 推到俾記者睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29be7775d44779580896221c7f6fddef1eed812","tid":1433990,"uid":209888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67c2218b5741d024f288cee755cd5418215511b","tid":1433990,"uid":253040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"推到記者跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426d5a55b1723d7c4faa9c68da0b31b17d6691b7","tid":1433990,"uid":238613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:44:04.000Z","msg":"成日話冇資料 日日開記招都唔準備好啲 咁開記招黎做咩 咩都答唔到<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢地成日答問題個時 一開始都唔係答問題 係講佢地想講嘅野先 同一定會駁去「暴力示威者」做左啲乜乜乜度 之後先答少少<br />\n<br />\n好似啲記者一問有關北角嘅問題 佢係即刻講返佢筆記入面準備好講嘅野先 完全唔係回應緊條問題"}]}